Use the standard library
This is how to fix_spaces of text:
   When isarray of text, then:
      The answer is text
   End when
   Remember that result is ""
   Remember that n is text's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that c is item i in text
      When c is 32, then:
         Add result to "_"
      But, if not:
         Add result to c
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
